<br>
Whenever I see or pass by a bard I usually stop and hand them one. When I tell them what it does (without reagent) they are more then happy. <br>
<br>
I agree it would be easier to require a Star Ruby, but that would shut out the Shaman community in terms of gate potions. The way the Dev team made this spell it both compliments (or at least satisfies) our Shaman brothers and sisters, and give us the ability to gate Melee’s to POK.  Not to mention it is easy for any shaman to combine these.<br>
<br>
Yes the level 4 reagent focus has a chance to proc and not use the component. However the steel wrist of strategy does not have a chance. So give them a QOK, Talisman and a Platinum necklace. <br>
<br>
To each his own, but I love this spell. <br>
